00:00:12.440 --> 00:00:20.919
It's definitely with mixed feelings that I
made the decision to retire after this season.

00:00:20.919 --> 00:00:25.730
I love those folks and I have loved my time
with them.

00:00:25.730 --> 00:00:28.919
I have loved working on this great repertoire
with them.

00:00:28.919 --> 00:00:34.110
Every year is a great, wonderful privilege
to live with that music and those singers

00:00:34.110 --> 00:00:39.600
and those players, that we can get past so
many technical things and go to the heart

00:00:39.600 --> 00:00:40.600
of music.

00:00:40.600 --> 00:00:44.910
And I will miss seeing those folks on a regular
basis.

